attributes.Long form description: The student is to disassemble the rolling cart. She starts from the bottom to disassemble the wheel of the rolling cart. The student turns over the rolling cart and then unscrews the hexagon cap nut and bolt. Next, the student removes the bracket and the tray. Then the student disassembles the bar and the base frame. Lastly, the student puts them together on the table neatly.
